    <entry>
      <title>Let&#39;s live each day that belongs to us</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/03/Let&#39;s%20live%20each%20day%20that%20belongs%20to%20us/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/03/Let&#39;s%20live%20each%20day%20that%20belongs%20to%20us/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="English"><a href="#English" class="headerlink" title="English"></a>English</h1><p>Life is a rhythm</p><p>There must be light and shadow</p><p>Left is right</p><p>Have a sunny with snow</p><p>Taste is contained in this fierce and constant twists and turns</p><p>And the world we live in</p><p>It’s more like a cycle</p><p>In the time when it’s not being noticed</p><p>In the change of seasons</p><p>In the stars where the sun rises and the moon sets</p><p>If every corner of the earth were filled with light</p><p>Who needs stars</p><p>Who would look away at night</p><p>Looking for distant security</p><p>When tomorrow is today</p><p>Today is yesterday</p><p>And finally become a day that no longer matters in my memory</p><p>Don’t talk about how things have changed</p><p>Time always learns not to wait</p><p>There is only now to cherish</p><hr><h1 id="Chinese"><a href="#Chinese" class="headerlink" title="Chinese"></a>Chinese</h1><p>生活是种律动</p><p>须有光有影</p><p>有左有右</p><p>有晴有雪</p><p>滋味就含在这猛而不变的曲折里</p><p>而我们生活的世界</p><p>更像是一种轮回</p><p>在不被注意的时间里</p><p>在四季的变化中</p><p>也在这日升月落的繁星里</p><p>如果大地的每个角落都充满了光明</p><p>谁还需要星星</p><p>谁还会在夜里遥望</p><p>寻找遥远的安稳</p><p>当明天变成今天</p><p>今天成为昨天</p><p>最后成为记忆里不再重要的一天</p><p>不要再谈事过境迁</p><p>时间它始终学不会等待</p><p>能珍惜的只有现在​</p><hr><h1 id="End"><a href="#End" class="headerlink" title="End"></a>End</h1><p>Let’s call it a day and wish you a better day tomorrow</p><p>Good night</p>]]></content>
      
      
